{"prompt": "Generate a website for a podcasting network. The website should be innovative and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Nebula Podcasts</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0077cc;\n            --secondary-color: #e6f2ff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --bg-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #005fa3;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--accent-color) 100%);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 2;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card {\n            background-color: var(--bg-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 180px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.6em;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555555;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .podcast-card a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            h2 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Nebula Podcasts</h1>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; position: relative; z-index: 2;\">Explore the universe of sound.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Featured Podcasts</h2>\n        <div class=\"podcast-grid\">\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/0077cc/ffffff?text=Cosmic+Chronicles\" alt=\"Cosmic Chronicles Podcast Cover\">\n                <h3>Cosmic Chronicles</h3>\n                <p>Journey through the vastness of space, exploring celestial events, alien encounters, and the future of humanity among the stars.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/005fa3/ffffff?text=Quantum+Leap\" alt=\"Quantum Leap Podcast Cover\">\n                <h3>Quantum Leap</h3>\n                <p>Dive into the mind-bending world of quantum physics, explained in an accessible way. Understand the universe's smallest building blocks.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/0077cc/ffffff?text=Galactic+Guild\" alt=\"Galactic Guild Podcast Cover\">\n                <h3>Galactic Guild</h3>\n                <p>Follow the adventures of intergalactic traders, bounty hunters, and explorers in this fictional sci-fi saga.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n             <div class=\"podcast-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x180/005fa3/ffffff?text=Starship+Stories\" alt=\"Starship Stories Podcast Cover\">\n                <h3>Starship Stories</h3>\n                <p>Real-life accounts and fascinating tales from those who have traveled beyond Earth's atmosphere.</p>\n                <a href=\"#\">Listen Now</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Nebula Podcasts. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}